through the normal validation procedure. This is especially useful
for boolean flags on existing records.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/blockquote&gt;
&lt;p&gt;If you need validations you can just use update_attributes.&lt;/p&gt;&lt;/div&gt;</body-html>
